✅ 方案3：SSH 拉日志 → 本地生成图片
# ssh_log_to_image.py
import paramiko
from PIL import Image, ImageDraw, ImageFont

HOST = "your_server_ip"
USER = "your_user"
PASSWORD = "your_password"
REMOTE_LOG = "/tmp/test.log"

# 连接SSH
ssh = paramiko.SSHClient()
ssh.set_missing_host_key_policy(paramiko.AutoAddPolicy())
ssh.connect(HOST, username=USER, password=PASSWORD)

stdin, stdout, stderr = ssh.exec_command(f"cat {REMOTE_LOG}")
content = stdout.read().decode()

ssh.close()

# 转图片
lines = content.split("\n")

font_size = 16
line_height = font_size + 4
img_width = 1200
img_height = line_height * len(lines) + 20

img = Image.new("RGB", (img_width, img_height), color="black")
draw = ImageDraw.Draw(img)

try:
    font = ImageFont.truetype("DejaVuSansMono.ttf", font_size)
except:
    font = ImageFont.load_default()

y = 10
for line in lines:
    draw.text((10, y), line, fill="white", font=font)
    y += line_height

img.save("ssh_log.png")

print("✅ ssh_log.png 已生成")
✅ 方案4（🔥最推荐）：Flask + Playwright（企业环境最佳）
🔹 Flask 服务（展示日志）
# app.py
from flask import Flask, Response

app = Flask(__name__)

LOG_FILE = "test.log"

@app.route("/log")
def show_log():
    with open(LOG_FILE, "r", encoding="utf-8") as f:
        content = f.read()

    html = f"""
    <html>
    <body style="background:black;color:white;font-family:monospace;">
    <pre>{content}</pre>
    </body>
    </html>
    """
    return Response(html, mimetype="text/html")

if __name__ == "__main__":
    app.run(host="0.0.0.0", port=5000)

启动：

python app.py
🔹 Playwright 截你自己的页面
# screenshot_local_page.py
from playwright.sync_api import sync_playwright

URL = "http://127.0.0.1:5000/log"

with sync_playwright() as p:
    browser = p.chromium.launch(headless=True)
    page = browser.new_page()

    page.goto(URL)
    page.wait_for_timeout(2000)

    page.screenshot(path="log.png", full_page=True)

    print("✅ log.png 已生成")

    browser.close()
🔥 最终推荐架构（适合你公司内网）

结合你现在的需求（GitLab + pipeline + 内网）：

GitLab pipeline
    ↓
远端服务器生成 log.txt
    ↓
Flask 提供 /log
    ↓
Playwright 截图
    ↓
生成报告图片
⚠ 关键建议（非常重要）

👉 不要再死磕 GitLab UI 截图，原因：

SSO / MFA 验证
cookie 过期
内网限制
UI 经常变

👉 本质上 GitLab 是“反自动化”的

